What I am trying to say is

121
00:08:18,500 --> 00:08:19,820
now that you are back,

122
00:08:20,020 --> 00:08:21,780
it means Summer Time

123
00:08:22,020 --> 00:08:22,820
will be popular once again.

124
00:08:23,980 --> 00:08:24,539
Again?

125
00:08:24,820 --> 00:08:25,380
Yes.

126
00:08:25,620 --> 00:08:26,260
It used to be popular?

127
00:08:26,380 --> 00:08:28,179
It was so popular back then.

128
00:08:28,500 --> 00:08:31,059
It's all because of your signature dessert,

129
00:08:31,140 --> 00:08:32,419
Summer's Kiss.

130
00:08:35,020 --> 00:08:36,060
Now I remember.

131
00:08:37,460 --> 00:08:39,540
One day before you went missing,

132
00:08:39,540 --> 00:08:41,140
you made a Summer's Kiss.

133
00:08:41,340 --> 00:08:42,540
You put it there.

134
00:08:43,300 --> 00:08:44,380
Then, you left the store.

135
00:08:44,380 --> 00:08:45,300
You told me

136
00:08:45,300 --> 00:08:47,860
