167
00:10:38,340 --> 00:10:39,020
Xu Xiao Dong.

168
00:10:40,460 --> 00:10:41,180
What is he doing here?

169
00:10:42,660 --> 00:10:44,700
What are you doing here?

170
00:10:49,780 --> 00:10:50,860
[What am I doing here?]

171
00:10:54,820 --> 00:10:56,020
Chu Xia, help me out.

172
00:10:56,300 --> 00:10:56,980
Let's move this table

173
00:10:56,980 --> 00:10:58,420
