197
00:11:59,920 --> 00:12:01,020
[You have received 500,000 yuan]

198
00:12:01,020 --> 00:12:02,260
[You have received 500,000 yuan]
That's too much.

199
00:12:02,780 --> 00:12:03,500
Look.

200
00:12:04,060 --> 00:12:05,180
Look at this.

201
00:12:05,180 --> 00:12:06,220
But we can't accept the money.

202
00:12:07,540 --> 00:12:08,340
You know him, right?

203
00:12:08,340 --> 00:12:09,260
Return the money to him.

204
00:12:11,700 --> 00:12:12,700
You can't do so.

205
00:12:13,100 --> 00:12:14,820
I don't really know Winter.

206
00:12:14,820 --> 00:12:16,420
I am only in charge of

207
00:12:16,420 --> 00:12:18,900
the business of his company.

208
00:12:19,060 --> 00:12:20,740
