233
00:13:30,620 --> 00:13:31,740
Chu Xia.

234
00:13:32,220 --> 00:13:34,460
That's so well said.

235
00:13:34,500 --> 00:13:36,060
My bank card

236
00:13:36,060 --> 00:13:38,860
