237
00:13:39,940 --> 00:13:41,380
I'm willing to give you some courage.

238
00:13:45,980 --> 00:13:46,700
Go away.

239
00:13:46,940 --> 00:13:48,540
Go away. I want to sit here.

240
00:13:49,420 --> 00:13:50,860
Chu Xia, think about it.

241
00:13:50,940 --> 00:13:52,700
Since Winter is being so supportive,

242
00:13:52,860 --> 00:13:54,700
we should

243
00:13:54,700 --> 00:13:55,820
