247
00:14:00,740 --> 00:14:01,420
He...

248
00:14:02,020 --> 00:14:03,020
We must not accept the money.

249
00:14:05,220 --> 00:14:05,820
Chu Xia.

250
00:14:06,300 --> 00:14:07,500
