253
00:14:11,900 --> 00:14:13,180
Am I right, Xiao Dong?

254
00:14:13,300 --> 00:14:14,980
Yes.

255
00:14:17,020 --> 00:14:17,660
Chu Xia,

256
00:14:17,940 --> 00:14:18,820
